{"tid":239163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估報紙]姦劫女生：USB線愈出愈韌　頻用於強姦自殺","createTime":"2017-05-11T13:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T15:35:51.000Z","uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5673598ce580c01dbb6cb3b803385bb577f100ff","tid":239163,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"九龍灣姦劫案疑犯在警署內，疑用電腦USB線自殺身亡。巧合的是，案發時用來綁起女事主的工具，亦同是一條電腦USB線。有工程師指出，電腦USB線可承受多達100磅拉力！事實上，將電腦USB線用作自殺或綑綁的案件，過往屢見不鮮。<br />\n<br />\n市面上售賣的電腦USB線可謂愈出愈耐用，一些甚至採用特強尼龍物料製成，更趨堅韌。香港理工大學機械工程學系前工程師盧覺強表示，因USB線內有銅線、纖維膠包裹，外面還有絕緣膠套着，加起來拉力會增強，而「尼龍編織線更堅固！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，他認為一般USB線雖能承受100磅拉力，但用以上吊或未必有足夠的承托力，因一般男性約有140磅，他推斷若用USB線上吊，會一吊就斷。「如果是綁着頸，用手扯緊頸項扯到斷氣，就會有這種可能！」<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，以電腦線用作上吊或犯案事件，過往在中港台屢次發生。去年一名浸大女學生，疑不堪學業壓力，在大埔廣福公園球場女廁以USB線上吊自殺身亡。2010年，一名內地女尖子疑不堪學業壓力與情傷雙重打擊，在中大宿舍內用USB線纏頸上吊身亡。2015年，台灣一名23歲男子，以USB線勒住一名夜歸女頸部，企圖拖到草叢性侵，幸該男子最終因膽怯而放棄。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170511/bkn-20170511165717891-0511_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170511%2Fbkn-20170511165717891-0511_00822_001.html&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fcca0bb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170511/bkn-20170511165717891-0511_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"05677cff71557120f808d15f038c6989e776375c","tid":239163,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfe08548b2a82e95ebe3bed6e0d2da7d7e46c4f","tid":239163,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"韌到吊到頸 但又脆到扯得斷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94840140322feccda24acff3fd331052e911349","tid":239163,"uid":70832,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韌到吊到頸 但又脆到扯得斷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 用線勒死佢，同吊起黎個重量點同丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee2db06e19763271e233ca5e1bd778feb193cc3","tid":239163,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C158flZVQAAzP8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC158flZVQAAzP8y.jpg&h=f078235d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"982fce822f6eb6f7ea98e1d212c1615135c08a52","tid":239163,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:24:02.000Z","msg":"警察官方報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f12b959f3424289112d9dc7385284ad8fdb0d84","tid":239163,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"果個犯成百五六磅 , 用黎吊頸 條usb 線一定會斷"},{"pid":"5d289dd11d907012f9aff12cf4a2026efab9721d","tid":239163,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb00fd4ab52479c5a3447d0a8a43362ec2e3aa3f","tid":239163,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:06:46.000Z","msg":"白粉 垃圾蘋果都有報"},{"pid":"70b04cb37a6ed93453cdd3ce3f08b59454bc637d","tid":239163,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C158flZVQAAzP8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC158flZVQAAzP8y.jpg&h=f078235d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nMicheal can't save himself <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7a8a295460a313cb717db91519a6b6b7d78675","tid":239163,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:25:06.000Z","msg":"要列入攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"25454374917474752c76813a565ef9f77306